snippet.title: Cobots - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Out now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1342660/Cobots/

Challenge yourself to overcome tricky puzzles in Cobots! A cute single-player puzzle game where you have to collaborate with your previous attempts! Delve into a colorful world filled with a variety of dangers and obstacles, and help these robots find the true meaning of life.
Planned to be released in April 2021!

Check us out on:
Discord: https://discord.gg/ER97YWb
Twitter: https://twitter.com/subfrost_games
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/user/SubfrostInteractive
Our website: https://subfrostinteractive.com/

Credits:
Adam Wallberg - Director, Programmer, & Composer
Sanna Wallberg Ylvén - UI & Environment Artist
Cecilia Bullarsjö - Art Lead, 3D Artist
Felix Grönvall - Design Lead, Level Designer
Markus Kromli - Level Designer
Kurt Areskoug - Audio Engineer & Programmer

#Cobots #Steam #PuzzleGame
